MANUAL STEPS

* Make symlinks to the following:

ln -s _home/.zshrc.d ~/.zshrc.d
ln _home/.ackrc ~/.ackrc
ln _home/.gitconfig ~/.gitconfig
ln _home/.gitignore ~/.gitignore
ln _home/.zshenv ~/.zshenv
ln _home/.zshrc ~/.zshrc
ln _home/.irbrc ~/.irbrc

* Give TextMate consistent shortcuts:

System Preferences > Keyboard > Keyboard Shortcuts
  Application: TextMate
    Menu Title: Previous File Tab
    Shortcut: Command-Shift-[

    Menu Title: Next File Tab
    Shortcut: Command-Shift-]

